title: Lakeside 2 Bedroom Apartment Near Rainbow Beach
posting_body: ["O'Toole Tower Apartments  -  7701 S. South Shore Drive", "This elevator Apartment Building is in a great location by Lake Michigan's Rainbow Beach and Park.", "You can enjoy lake views and South Shore's Park Recreation facility.", 'Units are newly decorated and include a Stove, Refrigerator, Air-Conditioner, Carpeting, Ceiling Fans and Blinds.', 'Both heat and cooking gas are FREE -- electric is not included.', 'Gated Off Street Parking for an additional charge per month (assigned spots and gated lot).', '-Monthly rent for 1 Bedroom - $775', '-Monthly rent for a 2 Bedrooms, 1 bath - $975', '-Monthly rent for a 2 Bedrooms, 1.5 baths - $1025', 'One bedroom -- $350 non-refundable move-in fee after application is approved.', ' No security deposit', 'Two bedroom -- $500 non-refundable move-in fee after application approval.', ' No security deposit.', '$40 non-refundable application fee for credit and background check.', 'Please call KALABICH MANAGEMENT at (708) 424-4216 for availability and to set up an appointment.', 'Rental office hours are Monday through Friday 8:00 a.m. until 5:00 p.m and Saturdays from 8:00 a.m. until 12:00 noon by appointment.', 'You can also check us out on Facebook, our website <URL>, or Twitter (@KalabichMgmt).']
